---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | ReformaT Venezuela" description="ReformaT Venezuela privacy policy. How we protect and use your personal data." activePage="contact">
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="legal-title">Privacy <span class="gold">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>At ReformaT Venezuela we collect information you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact us through the contact form (name, email, phone, message)</li>
          <li>Request a quote or consultation</li>
          <li>Communicate with us via WhatsApp or email</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information solely to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and quote requests</li>
          <li>Provide advice on your remodeling project</li>
          <li>Contact you to coordinate technical visits</li>
          <li>Improve our services and customer support</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>Your personal information is treated with the utmost confidentiality. We do not share, sell, or transfer your data to third parties without your express consent.</p>

        <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses essential technical cookies for its operation and anonymous analytical cookies to improve user experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data that we have stored</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to the processing of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:contacto@reformat-venezuela.online">contacto@reformat-venezuela.online</a></p>

        <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to update this privacy policy. Any changes will be published on this page with the corresponding update date.</p>

        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: contacto@reformat-venezuela.online</li>
          <li>WhatsApp: +58 422-799-7043</li>
          <li>Service area: Valencia, San Diego, Carabobo and Caracas</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 180px 0 100px;
    background: var(--white);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .legal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .legal-updated {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gray-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 3rem 0 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .legal-content h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .legal-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .legal-content ul {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem 2rem;
  }
  .legal-content li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .legal-content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page { padding: 140px 0 60px; }
    .legal-content h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .legal-content p, .legal-content li { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
</style>